imdb.plot outline: Elite Model Look is the largest and most successful modeling competition in the world that has launched the careers of some of the biggest names in the business including Cindy Crawford, Stephanie Seymour, Gisele Bundchen, Adriana Lima & Alessandra Ambrosio. ELITE NEW FACE is a 10 part documentary series taking you behind the scenes of the biggest casting event in the Fashion Calendar. We will follow the intensely emotional adventure of a group of contestants as they progress through the competition, from regional castings all the way to the World Final and, for the lucky winners, their first professional assignment.
